"{\"uid\": \"afaqs.com-news-advertising-googles-olympics-ad-for-ai-is-under-fire-but-is-the-heat-justified\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"0  By clicking the button, I accept theTerms of Use of the serviceand itsPrivacy Policy, as well as consent to the processing of personal data.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not have an account?Signup  Powered by :  Follow Us  A screengrab from Google's latest ad  Viewers are calling out Google for sneaking AI into authentic human moments.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts weigh in.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the midst of the Paris Olympics' grandeur and athleticism, an unexpected controversy has emerged, not on the track or in the pool, but in the commercial breaks between events.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Google, one of the world's leading tech giants, has found itself at the centre of a heated debate over its latest advertisement, which aimed to showcase the company's artificial intelligence capabilities but instead sparked concerns about the role of AI in our daily lives.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The advertisement, which has been airing during Olympic broadcasts, presents a heartwarming scene of a father describing his daughter's admiration for American track star Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999709743865, \"rank\": 2.593825117027221e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 960, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999998787179794, \"rank\": 1.2127212789906135e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young girl is shown enthusiastically training to emulate her hero, utilising hurdling technique tips generated by Google's AI search feature.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, the ad seems to strike a chord with viewers, portraying a touching story of inspiration and determination.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the controversy arises in the ad's final moments.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of encouraging his daughter to pen her own heartfelt letter to the athlete, the father turns to Google's Gemini chatbot, asking it to generate a message on behalf of the child.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The AI-crafted letter includes a bold claim about the girl's ambition to break McLaughlin's world record, a statement that many viewers found disconcerting when coming from an artificial source rather than the child herself.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing that Google Gemini AI ad really hurt my heart as someone who has taught writing to many young kids.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suggesting a child that young should use AI to write a letter to their Olympic hero is  a suggestion to steal important experiences from that child  - Jamilah Thompkins-Bigelow (@jtbigelow)July 28, 2024    Google AI ad during the Olympics about a young girl using Gemini to write a letter to an Olympian that inspires her and I think it's time to take tech back to 1986 because what the hell  - joe bro (@jbromovies)July 27, 2024    Google's intention was clear: to demonstrate the advanced capabilities of its AI in producing human-like text.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9999999983938324, \"rank\": 1.6064865438058718e-09, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}, {\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.633936502142389, \"rank\": 0.5184504438436794, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the execution has left many viewers uncomfortable, questioning the wisdom and ethics of replacing a child's genuine expression with computer-generated content.\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The backlash has been swift and significant, with social media platforms buzzing with criticism and concern.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This incident is not isolated in the tech world's recent advertising mishaps.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a few months prior, Apple, another tech behemoth, found itself in a similar predicament with its iPad Pro commercial.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2755, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3247677350235583e-24, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1802926141472283e-34, \"text\": \"iPad Pro\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The advert depicted various objects- ranging from musical instruments to books and typewriters -being crushed by a hydraulic press, only to be transformed into the sleek new tablet.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While intended to be a clever metaphor for technological progress, the ad struck a sour note with many viewers.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics, including renowned actor Hugh Grant, denounced it as symbolising \\\"the destruction of the human experience\\\", arguing that it glossed over the value of traditional tools and methods of creativity.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.486184753619068e-23, \"text\": \"Hugh Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also Read:Apple apologises for the iPad Pro 'crush' ad  These advertising missteps by Google and Apple have reignited a broader, more profound discussion about the impact of AI on society and employment.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3247677350235583e-24, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1802926141472283e-34, \"text\": \"iPad Pro\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IPad_Pro\"}, {\"begin\": 3438, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 3449, \"end\": 3454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3247677350235583e-24, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 3526, \"end\": 3528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The public's reaction reflects a growing unease about the rapid integration of AI into various aspects of life.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are questioning whether this relentless push for AI adoption is coming at the cost of authentic human experiences, creativity, and expression.\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3722, \"end\": 3724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The concern extends beyond just creative endeavours.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is widespread speculation and anxiety about how artificial intelligence might reshape the job market across various industries.\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will AI replace human workers in certain fields?\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How will it change the nature of work?\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These ads, whether intentionally or not, seem to have touched a nerve, adding fuel to the fire of these existing anxieties.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In light of these controversies, industry experts have weighed in on the debate, offering their perspectives on the ads and their implications.\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Naresh Gupta, co-founder at Bang in the Middle, a creative agency, offers a critical view of Google's Olympic ad, saying, \\\"Brands and advertisers live in a bubble, they live in their own world.\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4361, \"end\": 4367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0100579588422765e-31, \"text\": \"Naresh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allari_Naresh\"}, {\"begin\": 4368, \"end\": 4373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4454, \"end\": 4460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Disconnected from reality and only see what they want to see.\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Google, search and data is the only way to look at the world and this is what we see in this ad.\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4621, \"end\": 4627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so shocking to see human endeavour, perseverance, desire for excellence and scaling new peaks being reduced to an AI generated letter, only because Google wants to sell its wares.\\\"\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4837, \"end\": 4839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 4871, \"end\": 4877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naresh Gupta  Gupta further elaborates on what he believes should be the proper role of AI, suggesting, \\\"AI is a tool.\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 5023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4912, \"end\": 4917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4919, \"end\": 4924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9999985326878083, \"rank\": 1.4668220432947307e-06, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}, {\"begin\": 4993, \"end\": 4995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can help you get better.\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can help you craft something nice when you want a nudge.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Humanity cannot be driven robotically, the whole point of an 'assistant' is to have assistance.\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ideally, Google should have partnered father and Gemini to arrive at the wishes for her daughter.\\\"\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5217, \"end\": 5223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 5257, \"end\": 5263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9999999983938324, \"rank\": 1.6064865438058718e-09, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not all industry voices are critical of the commercial.\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vikash Chemjong, CCO at Cheil India, offers a more nuanced view, highlighting some positive aspects of the Google ad.\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5390, \"end\": 5393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\", \"score\": 0.9999921127393462, \"rank\": 7.875996774514426e-06, \"text\": \"CCO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_creative_officer\"}, {\"begin\": 5403, \"end\": 5408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.99964431761244, \"rank\": 0.00034295605664708676, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 5480, \"end\": 5486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He argues, \\\"There are so many positive things to it - the father daughter love.\", \"from\": 5491, \"to\": 5570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sporty daughter.\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her focus and determination.\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The father's effort to egg her on.\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, it's warm and emotional.\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the so many things that are right for the film some have still managed to find a wrong!\\\"\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vikas Chemjong  Chemjong also questions the basis of the backlash, drawing parallels with other technological advancements, \\\"When you show people using a washing machine to wash clothes, I am not sure how it undermines the ability of humans to wash clothes.\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 6042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5785, \"end\": 5790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\", \"score\": 0.7980049875309648, \"rank\": 0.2531249999999833, \"text\": \"Vikas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vikas_(rocket_engine)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or their ability to reach from point A to B when we advertise a bike.\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the point of technology was that it helps us do things better, faster, easier.\\\"\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the controversy continues to unfold, Google has inadvertently found itself in the midst of a significant communications crisis.\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6244, \"end\": 6250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9600144965793946e-19, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tech giant, known for its innovative approach to marketing, is now at the mercy of its public relations team as it grapples with the backlash.\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This situation raises important questions about crisis management in the age of social media: How can a brand recuperate from such a situation?\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What are the right steps to take to minimise the damage and rebuild trust with consumers?\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarunjeet Rattan, managing partner at Nucleus PR, offers insights into how the company might navigate these turbulent waters.\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6755, \"end\": 6762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\", \"score\": 0.9999995645376696, \"rank\": 4.345493868205197e-07, \"text\": \"Nucleus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeping\"}, {\"begin\": 6763, \"end\": 6765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.672302355289454e-30, \"text\": \"PR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_relations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An apology note saying they made a mistake was a good idea.\", \"from\": 6846, \"to\": 6906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is only the start,\\\" Rattan suggests.\", \"from\": 6907, \"to\": 6952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This campaign struck a deep chord amongst consumers who are already deeply divided and concerned about the growth of AI in a direction that seeks to replace them.\\\"\", \"from\": 6953, \"to\": 7117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7071, \"end\": 7073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4868198895210773e-22, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rattan emphasises the importance of active engagement and transparency in addressing the concerns raised by consumers.\", \"from\": 7119, \"to\": 7237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7119, \"end\": 7125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.82509418491971e-40, \"text\": \"Rattan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She advises, \\\"Do not ignore customer feedback.\", \"from\": 7238, \"to\": 7284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just offering platitudes is not enough.\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Be smart and offer consumers a direct feedback track that your team can listen to and work upon.\\\"\", \"from\": 7325, \"to\": 7422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking towards future campaigns, Rattan stresses the importance of demonstrating that the company has taken the feedback to heart.\", \"from\": 7424, \"to\": 7555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7458, \"end\": 7464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.82509418491971e-40, \"text\": \"Rattan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rattan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Course correct and showcase that change in the next campaign,\\\" she recommends.\", \"from\": 7556, \"to\": 7635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Demonstrate that you heard the consumers and are actually paying heed to the feedback and going back to your core professed mission.\", \"from\": 7636, \"to\": 7769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will go a long way in winning back consumers and also create a different line of progress that they resonate with.\\\"\", \"from\": 7770, \"to\": 7890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe to our Newsletter!\", \"from\": 7898, \"to\": 7926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  If you liked this article share it with your friends.they will thank you later\", \"from\": 7932, \"to\": 8030, \"entities\": []}]}"